    "text": [
        "Dear Sir or Madam,",
        "My name is Shyam. I am from Hyderabad. I have recently checked your brochure on one-week walking tour in mountains and am writing to you to know more information about the trip.",
        "Since my childhood, I have been thrilled to take part in walking trips in mountains which gives me a fresh breath of air and refreshment that gives a break from my daily chores.",
        "I wonder if you could provide me more information about the tour such as the start and end dates, the cost it incurs, things to carry and any important information to know ahead of the trip.",
        "Lastly, there are few concerns about my fitness level that I would like to express and get your advice before committing the trip. I have been not part of these kind of trips for a while due to my busy schedules at work, also I am not training physically these days. As a result, my fitness levels are down and I am wondering if I can keep up the trip.",
        "It would be great if you let me know what level of fitness is needed to make the trip successful. Awaiting your reply.",
        "Yours Faithfully",
        "P Shyam Kumar"
